{"tid":893836,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎分享辭職之後間公司會做的事（不分好壞）","createTime":"2018-11-08T02:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T16:52:28.000Z","uid":205394,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"66005a7f742ac0e0694f82d625a2e19581bc0ef7","tid":893836,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"我未辭職（準備辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n突然想起唔少從朋友到聽返黎既辭職之後遇到既事<br />\n有好事都有衰野<br />\n<br />\n好事：<br />\n有朋友跳槽去一間競爭對手公司，個老闆知道後重主題寫推薦信比佢<br />\n叫佢帶過去，等去到果邊更易受重用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n衰事：<br />\n有朋友轉工，老闆叫佢入房傾左一大餐人生哲理，最後加左個比佢轉工之後少既價叫佢留低，我朋友拒，佢就恐嚇佢話呢一行好細，日後有合作機會時會搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁多位有冇咩經歷一齊來分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc8f2e186fe1f4263d376ba77d6d91087302e0e","tid":893836,"uid":53798,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"衰事成日聽<br />\n<br />\n好事就睇下腦細有冇氣量, 有d會間中食下飯"},{"pid":"941e957c5b833dd41d845cb01685cc8276abb20a","tid":893836,"uid":131120,"like":13,"dislike":16,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"591380f4953f2edad2d0f499708ef6881b54cc4e","tid":893836,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"L,m"},{"pid":"c2553d25575692ac96c3406165efea8dc52c226b","tid":893836,"uid":126005,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"SL"},{"pid":"0dff338f818f8ecd266d7105ec3d43e20b4d194e","tid":893836,"uid":147892,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"quote":{"pid":"941e957c5b833dd41d845cb01685cc8276abb20a","tid":893836,"uid":131120,"like":13,"dislike":16,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:53:10.000Z","msg":"呢d就最on9<br />\n幾時都係 辭左職千祈唔好同人講去邊<br />\n幾熟都係 最多求其搵個藉口應酬左d同事<br />\n刊時真係開始做個陣先好同熟個d講"},{"pid":"b683ec674c4495ad3b8edeff3895f4d3fbe7df70","tid":893836,"uid":67272,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:37:58.000Z","msg":"[member]試過俾中年未婚痴肥閪分開我Last day <br />\n例計扣鐘星期五晏就3點走得<br />\n佢計我星期五返早上12點，下就唔洗返<br />\n星期六再返黎做半日先完<br />\n嬲撚到我仆街，打去勞工處問有無犯法<br />\n最後星期五返幾個鐘早上已經走得<br />\n好就係腦細祝我新工愉快話保持緊密聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  /member]"},{"pid":"fbdb32f4b14137a7d2a020cb18443574cfa49a7a","tid":893836,"uid":67272,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"b683ec674c4495ad3b8edeff3895f4d3fbe7df70","tid":893836,"uid":67272,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:37:58.000Z","msg":"[member]試過俾中年未婚痴肥閪分開我Last day <br />\n例計扣鐘星期五晏就3點走得<br />\n佢計我星期五返早上12點，下就唔洗返<br />\n星期六再返黎做半日先完<br />\n嬲撚到我仆街，打去勞工處問有無犯法<br />\n最後星期五返幾個鐘早上已經走得<br />\n好就係腦細祝我新工愉快話保持緊密聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  /member]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46476b66cc757b16a497410012639bfe71db72a7","tid":893836,"uid":4217,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:06:27.000Z","msg":"lastday比人點左去抹枱<br />\n做埋清潔<br />\n但明明我係office工黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91894cb73c75e8a351ebf91228766d1eed27274e","tid":893836,"uid":205394,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:30:08.000Z","msg":"有件唔知係好事定衰事<br />\n<br />\n識人辭職，佢知佢間公司人手唔夠<br />\n加上佢上司同老闆都係d好小器既人<br />\n<br />\n咁佢咪聽左人講辭職理由話係Family issue <br />\n點知平時除左不斷chur佢做野<br />\nOT到狗咁都做唔晒d野都照樣屌佢既上司老闆即時變到好關心佢<br />\n係咁問佢咩事呀，有冇野幫到手<br />\n佢唔講（因為根本無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）就係咁呵佢<br />\n又打晒感情牌咩好關心佢架，同事一家親呀<br />\n之後就話不如停薪留職啦，family issue搞店後再黎返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩到咁大，咁佢唯有先講係搵到第二間更好offer想走<br />\n之後比人狂屌<br />\n<br />\n成件事我都唔知話邊一邊唔岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5eedafc091638ad9891c163fda3355267b1865","tid":893836,"uid":51747,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"辭職後調位，自己一個坐一間房入面，電腦無network access<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n捱一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983e26f3c3031e7f731ef0e9465f9973c0d5eb0d","tid":893836,"uid":31361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31d62420678227017be96b66dc27d8314eb1be5","tid":893836,"uid":125976,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:40:32.000Z","msg":"你：<br />\n老細我想辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老細：<br />\n好呀，你搵 HR 幫你安排啦。<br />\n返出去繼續做嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c66031e9c683d9f7262c595ed5e05f3908c9b7","tid":893836,"uid":38033,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"第一份工，上司好照顧我，老闆就老而不黎<br />\n<br />\n上司見到我一直catch up 唔到都知我唔岩做個行，遞信之後一直keep 住教我其他soft skills, 點樣對人，點樣應對辦公室政治，<br />\n到家陣都有keep 住搵佢請佢食飯，而家有幸有條靚都問佢點教下屬<br />\n<br />\n老闆就典型港資西老闆，人地冇手尾放工唔熄燈會屌鳩最細粒既同事，姐係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n遞信後就日日企係我附近睇我做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好彩呀頭照我，借啲意叫我開會然後拉住著草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1